          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1643200945937-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>cornflour</strong> to the<strong> marinated</strong> <strong>basa pieces</strong>, and give everything a good mix up so the basa pieces are fully coated in cornflour</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1643200977471-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1643200977471-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1643200977471-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1643200977471-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1643200977471-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a very generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> coated basa pieces</strong> and cook for 3-4 min on each side or until browned – this is your <strong>curried crispy basa</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1643200982100-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1643200982100-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1643200982100-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1643200982100-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1643200982100-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped mint </strong>and<strong> coriander</strong> to the <strong>turmeric rice</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>herby turmeric rice</strong></p><p>Serve your <strong>curried crispy basa </strong>on top of the <strong>herby turmeric rice </strong>and the <strong>quick-pickled red cabbage </strong>to the side</p><p>Dollop the <strong>mango yoghurt </strong>over everything</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
